Subject: Re: [T2] 72-74 EGR Filter

--- Richard Atwell wrote:

> The 72-74 filter has to bolt to the dual carb
 intake. (I think it should read 73-74 because I
 don't think 72 models had EGR).

Correct. 72 did not.

 
> I'm not sure where the 73-74 filter breaches the
engine tin.
 
The 73-74 filter is at the front of the engine. Front
is front.
One end of the filter bolts to #3 exhaust pipe. The
other end bolts to a pipe that goes thru the upper
front tin.
